title: Sushiko
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Japanese, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Japanese place with a separate printed vegan menu (20+ rolls) - ask for it. Has Tofutti cream cheese for sushi rolls, vegenaise for spicy sauce, vegan eel sauce, and makes faux-roe from amaranth seeds. Vegan sushi boat available. Miso soup is vegan but not the clear soup. Regular menu is meat and fish.
